summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting overhead and underground electrical distribution easements over portions of Government Lot 1, Section 11, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Lots 12 and 13, Cedar Park No. 5; Vacated South 128th Street; Section 4, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., Lots 10 and 11, Block 1, Cedar Park No. 3; tract 139, Assessor's Plat of Panorama Heights; Block 10 North Beach Addition; Section 13, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; Tract "A" of King County Short Plat No. 377036; Parcel "C" of King County Short Plat No. 8402857; Lot 1, King County Short Plat No. 181002; and Tract "A" of preliminary King County Short Plat No. 385068, and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
